# Requirement Rule

Write REQ in **Chinese**.

Create REQ documents under `docs/requirements/` using `REQ-TEMPLATE.md`.

REQ must define:

- Functional requirements (numbered)
- Non-functional requirements
- User flows
- Input / output definitions
- Edge cases
- Dependencies on other features
- Traceability to PRD

Do not write SPEC or code until REQ is reviewed against PRD scope.
